description: When I started the hunt today already the first boy agreed to take part in a little "interview". Was he thinking that it would be broadcasted on TV and he would get famous? I forgot to ask so I guess I will never know. But I asked him for his life, his job, wether he has a girlfriend and about his financial situation. He was quite open considering that he was talking to a stranger. He even allowed me a peak into his sex life. He looked quite young but was obviously willing to experiment. Perfect for me. I offered him an experience he wouldn´t forget. Well, he wasn´t as easy as I thought when we started to figure out his "financial compensation"...
title: Czech Hunter 118
